<taxonomicName id="D2F588CAFD0603BF38C83BE88511F9B5" authority="subsp. marginata" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." infraspecific-rank="subsp." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. integrifolia" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="species" species="integrifolia" subspecies="marginata">A. integrifolia subsp. marginata</taxonomicName>
. We consider 
<taxonomicName id="2C5E8BE20DC1BBBB19CC52C8BA92F272" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. marginata" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="species" species="marginata">
<emphasis id="DB4F77A775F03D7F85E06C09EE690F83" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">A. marginata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to be a distinct species, differentiated mainly by its variegated leaf blades and vestigial female bracts that are not accrescent in fruit vs. non variegated leaf blades and conspicuous female bracts that are accrescent in fruit in 
<taxonomicName id="71CF30BB662AB22DD3A785AAC2539B48" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. integrifolia" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="species" species="integrifolia">
<emphasis id="B6F3DA99024795540AF0D28C61935410" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">A. integrifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. We include as synonyms 
<taxonomicName id="8837894BA522F867C0D039F590CFEBF8" authority="subsp. panduriformis" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." infraspecific-rank="subsp." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. integrifolia" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="species" species="integrifolia" subspecies="panduriformis">A. integrifolia subsp. panduriformis</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="07A3B5AAEBCFA02B96C0C27C8F15BE47" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." infraspecific-rank="var." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. integrifolia var. crateriana" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="variety" species="integrifolia" variety="crateriana">A. integrifolia var. crateriana</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="15B6CA8B82C55F165B7BBD746BDAE6F4" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." infraspecific-rank="var." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. integrifolia var. saltuum" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="variety" species="integrifolia" variety="saltuum">A. integrifolia var. saltuum</taxonomicName>
because they have the same characters as 
<taxonomicName id="A0BBE91041169A168E77041DEAB734A1" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="A." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="A. marginata" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="85" rank="species" species="marginata">
<emphasis id="FF5921D75FD8728B850860900281BA48" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="85">A. marginata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
